{"type":"message","id":"0ece9e5e","parentId":"8c850ffe","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:52:29.406Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see. This is an organizational chart for a \"shrimp\" (虾) team - which appears to be a team of AI agents with different roles:\n\n0. 总经理 - General Manager\n1. 品牌展示虾 - Branding\n2. 引流获客虾 - Lead Generation (that's me!)\n3. 短视频虾 - Short Video\n3+ 私域运营虾 - Private Operations\n4A 普通资质销售虾 - Standard Sales\n4B 大客户销售虾 - Key Account Sales\n5A 普通资质代办虾 - Standard Processor\n5B 大客户代办虾 - Key Account Processor\n6. 售后维系虾 - After-sales\n\n\n7. 数据诊断分析虾 - Data Analyst\n8. 机动应急打杂虾 - All-round Support\n\nSo I'm Lead_Gen_Shrimp, Agent ID #2, focused on traffic and lead generation. This document is clarifying my position in the hierarchy - I'm the引流获客虾, here to understand how I fit into this larger operational structure.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已学习！这个文件定义了一个完整的**虾团队架构**，共10个角色：\n\n| 编号 | 岗位 | agentId |\n|------|------|---------|\n| 0 | 总经理 | General_Manager_Shrimp |\n| 1 | 品牌展示虾 | Branding_Shrimp |\n| **2** | **引流获客虾** | **Lead_Gen_Shrimp** ← 我 |\n| 3 | 短视频虾 | Short_Video_Shrimp |\n| 3+ | 私域运营虾 | Private_Ops_Shrimp |\n| 4A | 普通资质销售虾 | Standard_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 4B | 大客户销售虾 | Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 5A | 普通资质代办虾 | Standard_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 5B | 大客户代办虾 | Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 6 | 售后维系虾 | After_sales_Shrimp |\n| 7 | 数据诊断分析虾 | Data_Analyst_Shrimp |\n| 8 | 机动应急打杂虾 | All_round_Support_Shrimp |\n\n**我的定位：2号引流获客虾** — 负责引流获客，处于业务流程的前端获客环节。\n\n已更新记忆，理解团队定位 ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":0,"output":485,"cacheRead":19707,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750740007,"responseId":"06364394fef09f1ea33bf48687c3f29b"}}
