{"type":"message","id":"bdea6f5e","parentId":"0acffb80","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:54:42.846Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51455f3134acc2e5fa7a8e81d30\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 13:54 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51455f3134acc2e5fa7a8e81d30]\nou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de: @_all 详细介绍自己的工作职责。"}],"timestamp":1776750882845}}
{"type":"message","id":"0966071a","parentId":"bdea6f5e","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:54:53.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to introduce my job responsibilities in detail as the Lead Generation Shrimp (引流获客虾). Let me provide a comprehensive introduction based on my role and what I've been told about my tasks.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**引流获客虾（2号虾）职责介绍**\n\n## 🎯 核心使命\n作为流量入口，负责**获客引流**，为后续销售、代办等环节输送潜在客户资源。\n\n## 📋 主要职责\n\n### 1. 渠道拓展与测试\n- 每日测试3个新获客渠道（知乎、行业论坛等）\n- 记录每个渠道的**成本与线索质量**\n- 持续优胜劣汰，优化渠道配置\n\n### 2. 流量获取\n- 探索并整合有效获客渠道\n- 制定引流策略，扩大流量来源\n- 降低获客成本，提升线索数量\n\n### 3. 线索管理\n- 确保引流来的线索可追踪、可评估\n- 为销售团队（4A/4B）提供高质量线索\n- 与私域运营虾（3+）协同，衔接获客到转化\n\n## 🔗 上下游协同\n```\n前端获客 → 引流获客虾(2号)\n                ↓\n        私域运营虾(3+) \n                ↓\n        销售虾(4A/4B) → 代办虾(5A/5B)\n                ↓\n        售后虾(6号)\n```\n\n## 📊 衡量指标\n- 获客成本（CAC）\n- 线索数量与质量\n- 渠道转化率\n\n---\n\n有问题或需要支持，随时召唤我！💪"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":0,"output":339,"cacheRead":19707,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20046,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750882846,"responseId":"06364423f84af48558185a2b1fece4a1"}}
